#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid ""
"The free edition is the complete back-in-stock waitlist. <strong>Plogins "
"Waitlist PRO</strong> adds demand insight and automation:"
msgstr ""
"Die kostenlose Edition ist die vollständige Warteliste für wieder verfügbare"
" Artikel. <strong>Plogins Waitlist PRO</strong> ergänzt Nachfrage-Einblicke "
"und Automatisierung:"

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Category segmentation</strong> - include and exclude rules per "
"product category"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Kategorie-Segmentierung</strong> - Einschluss- und Ausschlussregeln "
"pro Produktkategorie"

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Scheduled and batched sends</strong> - stagger notifications by "
"batch size and interval"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Geplanter und gebündelter Versand</strong> - Benachrichtigungen nach"
" Batch-Größe und Intervall staffeln"

#. Found in description list item.
msgid "<strong>Double opt-in</strong> - confirmed, consent-friendly signups"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Double-Opt-in</strong> - bestätigte, einwilligungsfreundliche "
"Anmeldungen"

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Demand analytics</strong> - see what shoppers are waiting for and "
"prioritise restocks"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Nachfrage-Analysen</strong> - sieh, worauf Kunden warten, und "
"priorisiere Nachbestellungen"

#. Found in description header.
msgid "Plogins Waitlist PRO"
msgstr "Plogins Waitlist PRO"

