#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"Social-proof \"N shoppers are already waiting\" line above the form "
"(optional, customisable, singular/plural aware)"
msgstr ""
"Social-Proof-Zeile \"N Kunden warten bereits\" über dem Formular (optional, "
